{"tid":1854289,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府話用電子手扣做家局隔離","createTime":"2020-01-31T11:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T11:59:17.000Z","uid":294343,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aab308f9213ca70004d62358d055bcb9fede37f9","tid":1854289,"uid":294343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"邊個話防疫唔關政治，今次承機推出電子手扣，下次用喺邊，唔洗我講啦<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】政府研推電子追蹤手環作家居隔離 取代檢疫中心<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日（31日）在記者會中指，由於物色地點作檢疫中心過程中遇上困難，故政府將研究使用電子追蹤手環，當檢疫中心不勝負荷時，使用手環輔以定位技術，為需隔離人士作家居隔離。林鄭月娥指，創科局及科學園相關企業，已進行研究，預期下星期將有200套手環可以使用。<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200131&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60544811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200131%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60544811&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMQjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=f7b8ae71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200131%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60544811&h=3730f107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200131&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60544811</a>"},{"pid":"89d3119862e95d251ff8a9fe5ba76c02b466c9a3","tid":1854289,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武肺背後嘅第三次世界大戰：諜戰丶生化戰丶經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854117</a><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"301ce21fe239af46c32b2870d551bed4749ccdf7","tid":1854289,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"校長呀校長，你哋放過老師啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853605</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"550d1fc33c986e1bc125d4e31be5a5de5e601e2e","tid":1854289,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"到時套手環一定唔撚work"},{"pid"